Subdirectories:
---------------

src/            C++ source files, including implementation and header files
bld/            build directories, to hold files generated during compilation
  serial/       build directory for serial programs
  parallel/     build directory for parallel programs
bin/            location for installing executables
scripts/        utilities in languages other than C++
  bin/          bash script tools
  python/       python tools
  mathematica/  mathematica tools
examples/       simulation usage examples 
doc/            documentation
  manual/       ascii *.dox source files for manual pages
  html/         location for installing *.html web manual pages

Files:
------

README        brief introduction to package 
LICENSE       GPL license
CONTENTS      this file
setup         bash script for initial setup (README and documentation)
makefile      main makefile

